Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Header,,0,0,0,,{\i1\fade(0,250)\fscx93\fscy93}These fan-made subtitles are not for sale, rent or any profit whatsoever.\NPlease support official  {\i0}Snack World{\i1} anime releases in your home country.\N\NSee lumpstud.tumblr.com for certain translation notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.13,0:00:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Snack World, the hallowed\Nground of dreams and adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.08,0:00:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A world where dragons roam and\Npeople have smartphones!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pretty cool place, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.37,0:00:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...And my name's Chup.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.26,0:00:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My village was burnt down by the evil\Nland-destroying merchant, Vinegar Khan,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've embarked on a journey\Nto get my revenge 1000-fold!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.44,0:00:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The tickets to King Oyster City, where\NVinegar is, cost 20 million gillan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.15,0:00:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm on an adventure searching for\Nbig treasure to make loads of cash!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.26,0:00:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Chup humming theme song]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.31,0:00:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go on another big adventure today!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.36,0:01:06.57,EPTITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fade(290,462)\pos(641.6,556.4)\fscx108\fscy108\frx8\fry0}Ep. 6: The Cutlass That Can Tear Anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.44,0:01:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Chup giggles]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}[Mayone grumbles]{\i0}\N- Oink...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have never guessed Mayone's paper fan\Nsword would be the strongest weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.79,0:01:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Chup.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.82,0:01:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't we here to report to the king?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.83,0:01:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your mouth and get talking so we can get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.59,0:01:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Your majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.01,0:01:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What is it, Chup?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the Kraken's body is very squishy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to chop it will just bounce us back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.06,0:01:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Agh! My axe didn't like that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.32,0:01:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's squishy, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.19,0:01:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.98,0:01:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sort of like your earlobes?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Pepperon's cheeks?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.98,0:01:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, more like your belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.70,0:01:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe...like Princess Melora's bottom?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hehe...squishy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.57,0:01:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Any day now, Chup.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.99,0:02:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Your majesty, point is, we can't chop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.00,0:02:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, trying to get the\Nmoisturizing cream is all but a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.66,0:02:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we're giving up on our current quest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh, so tearing the beast is a lost cause, hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- Guess it's a given, are you giving up?\N- Mhm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.25,0:02:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nooo, my skin's so dry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't put up with this! Daddy, how's\Nthe moisturizing cream coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.02,0:02:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still getting it? Is it running late?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't stand this at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't hurry, your youthful Melora...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.27,0:02:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll start looking like a wrinkly old woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.86,0:02:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard her, Chup! Resume your quest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! I'll be sure to fully, flawlessly\Nget my hands on that moisturizing cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you brats...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Sighs]{\i0} Even after that, we still\Nhave to go to the Kraken again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.08,0:02:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Being real, we've got no strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.62,0:02:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We're really in a pinch now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like my grandmother says!
