Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A pinch is an opportunity. Pink-colored\Npanties are 20% better!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Grr...what does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that to say we need a 20% increase in femininity?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.43,0:03:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, of course! I'd help you with that...\Nif it was relevant to anything right now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't give up yet, there's still plenty\Nof opportunities rolling around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...where are they, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Opportuuunities, opportuuunities!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.86,0:03:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one rolling around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Chup yelps]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Carbonara's Weapon Store is holding a big campaign!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're giving away a cut--ass\Nthat can --ear anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Giving it away! First come, first serve!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.05,0:03:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Gasps]{\i0} "A cutlass that can tear anything?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We can use it to tear through the Kraken's limbs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.71,0:03:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,An opportunity really did roll by us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.92,0:03:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Haha, thank you! You're our savior, bullhorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You should roll around in\Nhopeless situations more often.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's dumb and you know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Carbonara!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you still have that "cutlass\Nthat can tear anything?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.61,0:03:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Chup, is it? Yes, it's still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Had a hunch you'd be stopping by here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we have it, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.53,0:04:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is usually worth 10 million gillan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but our campaign is putting it on\Ndiscount at 10 {\i1}thousand{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang, what a steal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This campaign must be a godsend for you, Chup!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Chup and Pepperon humming gleefully]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is such a simple scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite sketchy that they're discounting\Nit so much from 10 million gillan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll buy it, Mr. Carbonara!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah! I only have 9,500 gillan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.31,0:04:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh, it must be since I bought from the 16th Melora\NCard pack at the convenience store earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, super rare!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mayone, you think you can work\Npart-time here to cover the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! What are you blabbering about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have bought that stupid card!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Melora isn't stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what is it? Buying it or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- The seductive act might come in handy.\N- You should try it out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:05:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hnng...fine, I'll do it. Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think you could...change the price of\Nthe cutlass that can tear anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.97,0:05:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Meh. Alright, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.24,0:05:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,15 thousand gillan it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Gasps]{\i0} You made it more expensive...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about an opposite effect...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna tell me how my charm played into that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...if only it could be sold for 9,500 gillan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just gonna have to take defeat here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.36,0:05:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Mr. Carbonara.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That sword & shield you sold me\Nback then was a counterfeit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you talking about, and why now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It kind of put us in a lot of danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Haha...that's...very unfortunate...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no real evidence of them being fakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we have evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here it is. Take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It...it's time for a special limited-time offer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,N-now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You customers are very lucky, as we're offering a huge discount right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:06:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The item you've requested,\Npreviously 15 thousand gillan,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,will be sold for 9,500 gillan to the\Nfirst buyer! Only for a limited time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,0:06:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sweet! I'll buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's our lucky day!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.41,0:06:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You've sure changed your tune.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be able to get a clean tear with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- So cool!\N- Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Chup, now you can be on your\Nway and enjoy your new product!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.10,0:06:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mr. Carbonara!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The box seems small, but I'm sure\Nit'll be a very effective sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, people don't say it "can tear anything" for nothing! {## Means the same as the original "Well, it isn't called "can tear anything" for nothing!", but sounds more like natural English.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Chup, aren't you gonna open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.32,0:06:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.20,0:06:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Everyone gleaming]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:46.30,Sword,,0,0,0,,{\c&H375941&\frx30\fry352\frz18.43\fade(200,0)\3c&H70FCCE&\bord2\fscx38\fscy37\pos(457.6,453.2)}The cut-pass that can bear anything
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:49.00,Sword,,0,0,0,,{\c&H473035&\frz15.56\frx6\fry358\pos(256.4,417.2)\fscx77\fscy74\3c&H58A3A9&\bord3}The cut-pass that can bear anything
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.87,0:06:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaaaaaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:53.46,Sword,,0,0,0,,{\c&H473035&\frz15.56\frx6\fry358\pos(256.4,417.2)\fscx77\fscy74\3c&H58A3A9&\bord3}The cut-pass that can bear anything
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"The cut-pass that can bear anything?!"
Dialogue: 3,0:06:53.47,0:06:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So instead of "cutlass," it's "cut-pass,"\Nand instead of "tear," it's "bear?!"
