Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:06:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,N...no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been duped again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, it seems to be a pass\Nyou can equip and check
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,before making a purchase with a\NContinental Trade Association certification.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not necessarily that much of a coax.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What about that should we be\Nhappy about? It's entirely pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.01,0:07:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going right back to the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.52,0:07:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They've already closed for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! So that old man's gonna get away with\Nforcing us some damn thing we don't need? Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Still very irritated...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all going to think as one on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,About Mayone's "can swear over anything" thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What{\i0} was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm swearing, huh? You wanna go into detail on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,N-no, it's just that right there...to say, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...a-are kind of trapping me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We're right back where we started.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.08,0:07:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't hurry up, slay that\NKraken, and get the cream,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Melora's skin will... 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh, Melora's skin...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.39,0:07:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What is with you and that stupid girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.72,0:07:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Chup grunts]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Chup yelps]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be the one apologizing...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.26,0:07:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.61,0:08:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm okay. Thank you! Later, hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Penne! Pay back your last loan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Still hasn't learned, has he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Penne panting]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah, I'm scared...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.43,0:08:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.99,0:08:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Grunts]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.26,0:08:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm not the bad guy here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Striiike!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hahaha!\N- We got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The heck is this? Tch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.53,0:08:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We really should just go and tell them we can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.41,0:08:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We just don't have any effective\Nweapons against the Kraken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, acceptance is crucial for humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're a Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Gob-san grunts]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- Nuh-uh.\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nuh-uh! Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yelling "nuh-uh" won't get you out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have some plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our Chup!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a plan, I just haven't come up with it yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the polar opposite of having a plan!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Sigh]{\i0} Guess it's still a no-go...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hnn...we're in trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare just sob your faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cuz "impossible," "excuses," and "sleeping in"\Ndon't exist in Cinderella's vocabulary!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.49,0:09:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have the guts to invoke me again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander! No more excuses! Except\Nthat sleeping in sounds kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.66,0:09:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Grunts]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.88,0:09:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's been a while...\N- Oink...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been hearing a lot from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"We can't beat the Kraken!" "We can't find a sword!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mayone won't stop snapping at us!" It's annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not snapping! Besides, how long\Nhave you been eavesdropping on us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- But you're snapping right n...\N- Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You better not tell me you forgot\Nabout our special training!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:09:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Err...I didn't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't forget a day like that even if I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Eating ice cream with Princess Melora...aah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Guh! Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.03,0:10:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have some nerve to be\Nsleeping at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like my grandmother says!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A well-slept child is a well-kept child.\NA slept-in child is a better-kept child!
