Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Feels...nice...\N- Oink...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up after failing once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My troopers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Come hell or high water, you {\i1}will{\i0} push through to the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like my grandmother says!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.93,0:10:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always darkest before dawn sky.\NIt doesn't matter, so don't cry.
