Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, guess sometimes you {\i1}do{\i0} say decent things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaa, how'd that get through her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, you better be done\Nwith your bickering and whining.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'm gonna show you something you might like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.74,0:10:53.38,Header,,0,0,0,,{\pos(564,102)}"Trying to shake around the destroyer axe"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha, what's that strong axe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to say that it's the..."Destroyer?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.38,Header,,0,0,0,,"Trying to shake around the destroyer axe"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mhm, it's called the "Destroyer Axe!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.53,0:11:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's well-known as the "hatchet that can tear anything!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.46,0:11:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! That's our key to victory against the Kraken!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.08,0:11:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll fully, flawlessly flatten it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.97,0:11:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Panting]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.25,0:11:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up, wait up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Gasps]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy doesn't give up, does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad, she needs help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.39,0:11:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh...? Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.74,0:11:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You make a really good support!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Chuckling]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.75,0:11:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Pepperon, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.07,0:11:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hyah!\N- {\i1}[Gob-san grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.75,0:11:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Tartar chuckling]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be prepared...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah! What is this? I can't see anything!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh, help!! Guh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.64,0:11:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:11:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hero, thank you, as always...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone's bullying you, give us a shout!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- Thank you! Goodbye!\N- Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:07.58,Header,,0,0,0,,"The cut-pass that can bear anything"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.77,0:12:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The cut-pass that can bear anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Must have been from when we\Ntook care of this guy before...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.65,0:12:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,N-no...it's Penne, not me!! Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.66,0:12:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Rooster crowing]{\i0}
