Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.83,0:12:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Carbonara!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have the Destroyer Axe that can tear anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you, Chup, right on top of\Neverything. Wait just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.45,0:12:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hehe...I wouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That’s nothing to feign modesty over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Destroyer Axe. Ain't it a beauty?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.96,0:12:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Obtaining this is the least you can expect of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Cackling]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We need that to defeat the desert Kraken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A kraken? Well, with this Destroyer Axe,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you can {\i1}SHPANG{\i0} through just about anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I really wanna {\i1}SPANG{\i0} through the squishy Kraken!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nuh-uh, Chup. This thing only slices with a {\i1}SHPANG{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:13:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm planning on givin' that Kraken a nice {\i1}SPANG!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it, it's {\i1}SHPANG! SHPANG!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sooo...{\i1}SPANG{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No! It's {\i1}SHPANG!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sooo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We get it! Why are you so fixated on this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.95,0:13:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it goes {\i1}SHPANG{\i0}, or {\i1}SHPAT{\i0}, or {\i1}ZKAT{\i0}, or {\i1}GSAT!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever the hell it goes, just sell it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, well, I never really said it was for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much you ask, I'm not selling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? So you just want it to boast?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, can I equip the cut-pass that can bear anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Err, no, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pass certified by the\NContinental Trade Association, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't follow the rules, can\Nyou even keep this store open?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hnng...fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurrah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah, it can really tear anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, since it's an axe, Pepperon's gotta have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh, I can feel its power inside of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna slice that Kraken in two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Chup, you happy with yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Welp, later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi, Chup, where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to test it with the wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi, stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright, we'll just shake it around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oi, Chup!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Fitting it on for size!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Pepperon, that's dangerous, just make it a Jara.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm, but I want to keep it like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.19,0:14:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll wear yourself out before battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't even feel heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Hatchet, hatchet, my gigantic hatchet~ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you stop singing that awful song?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Sword, sword, my so-little sword~ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- You don't have to imitate him!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ This chest, this chest, this sweet home of mine~ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How lovely, heehee!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:42.98,mask,,0,0,0,,{\c&H0D0C0E&\p1\fade(50,0)}m 726 632 l 776 640 817 630 836 620 913 620 924 608 923 585 955 582 955 606 980 606 1009 561 1041 556 1051 590 1068 593 1081 588 1112 542 1121 497 1054 475 1019 526 995 515 918 532 862 520 820 523 811 544 715 537{\p0}
Dialogue: 2,0:14:40.80,0:14:42.98,MonsterName,,0,0,0,,{\c&H8D3BDE&\fade(50,0)\3c&H0D0C0E&\bord10\frz9.304\pos(931.2,617.2)\fscx423\fscy343}Mimic
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.80,0:14:42.98,MonsterName,,0,0,0,,{\c&H8D3BDE&\fade(50,0)\3c&HE7E8E9&\bord16\frz9.304\pos(931.2,617.2)\fscx423\fscy343\clip(m 972 500 l 1020 507 1041 478 955 464)}Mimic
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Haha! I've got prey! Four of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Laughing]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a treasure chest, right in the middle of the desert!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.64,0:14:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that seem very off?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't know for sure unless we open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- Well, I guess you're right...\N- {\i1}[Mimic laughing]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What'dya think is in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally, I really hope it's a pendant from Peffany!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be some food in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.19,0:15:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what it is, I hope I get a weapon for myself!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hahahaha! You'll only find Mimic inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, open it up, open it up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, how about we decide who gets the\Ncontents depending on what they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take it if it's a sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,For me if it's a pendant!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take any weapon that comes out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.00,0:15:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll take it if it's food!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who's gonna get eaten, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Did it move a bit just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be a legendary sword in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe a magic wand, or\Nany kind of wand, I'll take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.81,0:15:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.19,0:15:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But what would you guys need a wand for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.15,0:15:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I see your point...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We should just open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Grrr...ugh! How long are they gonna keep babbling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.57,0:15:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting in here forever!! Just open it up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.16,0:15:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...But it has a lock on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.84,0:15:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have something to unlock it with.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:15:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Chup!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I think we might have {\i1}something{\i0} for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you idiots understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Use that axe to break the lock and open the chest!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go "BOO!" and it'll be over for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.88,0:16:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm......
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?! Come on, figure it out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hmm...\N- Hyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My hatchet that can tear anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It can break the lock on the chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah, we {\i1}can{\i0} do that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, that's it, you can do it, do it! Hahahaha...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.33,0:16:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready...and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.63,0:16:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, here, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please be my sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to be my thing, I just know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy needs a new weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi-yaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.77,0:16:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAAAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.07,0:16:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pepperon, that's way too much!\NYou weren't supposed to cut the chest itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you've ruined whatever was in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, I got carried away...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My equipment...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But we've learned one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This axe is certified astounding!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. Let's move past the\Ntreasure and head to the Kraken!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me, Kraken!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Without fail, I'll give you a {\i1}SPA{\i0}- er, I mean, a {\i1}SHPANG!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,♪ Hatchet, hatchet, my gigantic hatchet~ ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.49,0:17:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bye!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.34,0:17:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Kraken groaning]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you here, Pepperon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid my hands won't stop\Nshaking in front of the enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do, Chup?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh...leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.36,0:17:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh??
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.82,0:17:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll keep the Kraken busy while you\Nchop its limbs with the Destroyer Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,G-got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.12,0:17:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Come at us, Kraken! We'll be taking\Nthat moisturizing cream this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.87,0:17:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[War cry]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Have some of my strongest...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.79,0:18:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You... hyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Kraken groaning]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you won't eat those moves, have a taste of Gobby!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.81,0:18:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice job!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Screaming]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Yelling]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.10,0:18:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Gasping]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm A-OK, by the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't lose to a squid anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think saying "squid" makes it angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Screaming]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.47,0:18:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- Guh.\N- Oof.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll knock this guy out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.42,0:18:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Gasps]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.88,0:18:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Don't sleep at a time like this!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.51,0:18:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Agh, this hurts...\N- Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- Chup!\N- {\i1}[Gasp]{\i0} Are you alright, Mayone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks to you dozing off! ...Well,\NI guess {\i1}that{\i0} was thanks to my spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.93,0:19:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hnng...now that it's come to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you big squid, who's not\Nactually a squid despite being one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're feeling absolutely fine and cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not fine and cool at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.14,0:19:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Sighs]{\i0} I feel like I'm gonna faint...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, squid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We should eat you dried! 'Cuz you're a squid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Shrieking]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Chup! Hnn... Oh, what's the point...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,, {\i1}[Coughs]{\i0} Pepperon! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Aight, I'm goin' in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.22,0:19:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[War cry]{\i0} Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.22,0:19:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Use your epic axe and give him a {\i1}SHPANG!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's what the other guy was talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi-yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.10,0:19:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}[Groaning]{\i0}\N- You did it!
