Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.90,0:21:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can make Melora's wish come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But if he's dead, where's the moisturizing cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.08,0:21:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}[Sighs]{\i0}\N- Oink...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So that didn't net us the cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.29,0:21:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we supposed to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.79,0:21:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,To get the moisturizing cream from the Kraken...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.75,0:21:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, this mystery only gets deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.54,0:21:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.46,0:21:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kraken, I'm so sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Err, we kinda needed your limbs, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,uhh, that's why we had to chop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose there's any meaning to\Nit drying up, right? 'Cuz you're a squid?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.28,0:21:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Roaring]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.69,0:21:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}[Screaming]{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.53,0:22:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Did it tear? Did it slice with a {\i1}SHPANG?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.95,0:22:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you'd expect, the\NDestroyer's power is the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.32,0:22:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll have that back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.86,0:22:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is farewell I suppose... {\i1}[sniffle]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.25,0:22:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Pepperon?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.18,0:22:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,An axe I'll have, an axe I won't.\NAn axe I'll have, an axe I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.11,0:22:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, come on, Pepperon...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.34,0:22:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be that heartbroken...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.92,0:22:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Pepperon, you still have an axe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.09,0:22:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So, cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.88,0:22:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,An axe I'll have, an axe I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.93,0:22:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}[Chup sighs]{\i0}\N- He's really hurt by this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.20,0:22:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best we just leave him be for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.31,0:22:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay.\N- Oink...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.24,0:22:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,An axe I...won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.03,0:22:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaaaagh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.16,0:22:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mayone!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.20,0:22:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you teach us about today?
