Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,slight differences in their color and/or shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.88,0:22:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't see them often!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.29,0:23:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of their spares availability,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.29,0:23:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it's something to be proud of finding!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.00,0:23:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, really?
